    <note>Xin(1) Zhongfu [737] His ancestors were Longxi jun Xin(1). He moved from Fenzhou, Xihe xian to Xuzhou, Changshe xian. Youze's [7243] grandfather. His grandson Youzhong's [3369] father-in-law was Ma(2) Liang [1349]. Youzhong's sons-in-law were Wang(2) Yu(2) [1931] and Ma(2) Yu [3670], who had the same generational name as Ma(2) Liang's [1349] grandsons. SS, 266.14b; Su Song, WJ, 58.1a, 61.12b; YLDD, 12306.19a, 24a. CBD, 1, 731-2.</note>
